The '''Big Boom''' was the [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] on [[Nova Station]]. It featured [[Bobolo Baker's All-Bith Band]]. After escaping from [[Galactic Alliance Guard|GAG]] custody, [[Ben Skywalker]] stopped on Nova Station to rendezvous with [[Trista Zel]] and [[Taryn Zel]], twin sisters in [[Hapan Security]], and to send [[Lon Shevu]]'s body to his wife, [[Shula Shevu]], on [[Vaklin]]. As they departed the station, they were ambushed by [[SD-XX]], who attempted to kill Ben, but was shoved out an airlock after a brief duel. The trio attempted to rendezvous with Prince [[Isolder]], but Isolder was captured and imprisoned on the [[Anakin Solo (starship)|''Anakin Solo'']].

